                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Willowmire boardwalk. One rotten plank and the bog keeps you. I watch the crossing so the trainers who reach Mystic reach it whole."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Titania keeps the Fairy gym past the reeds. Charming until she is not. Step careful."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Mind your footing. Mystic Marsh and the Fairy leader wait past the last plank."
                        }
                    ],
